## #reset-cells

**Value type:** `<u32>`

The *#reset-cells* property defines the number of cells required to encode a reset specifier for this reset controller. Used by reset controller nodes to indicate how many `<u32>` cells follow the phandle in `resets` references.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
gcc: clock-controller@100000 {
    compatible = "qcom,sm8550-gcc";
    #reset-cells = <1>;
};
```
